    <p>
      Mr. Pierson joined HCI as the CIO in August 2009. He was previously the CIO of Contexo Media LLC, a publisher of medical coding books and software. He also served as Vice President of Technology Development for Ingenix, a United Healthcare company. At Ingenix, he was responsible for all software development related to medical coding, Payor and Provider claims editing, Property & Casualty applications, and patient prescription history products. In addition, he oversaw internal business systems, CRM, web and ecommerce development activities. Prior to Ingenix, Mr. Pierson worked for ProQuest in Ann Arbor, MI for 11 years. He served there in a variety of positions, including Vice President of Publisher Services, Field Sales Executive, Product Manager, and Director of Strategic Alliances.
